{"tid":2326001,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 焗葡國非洲雞上腿 配 辣椰香葡汁 拼 燒煙肉著仔沙律","createTime":"2020-12-15T04:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T08:17:57.000Z","uid":33359,"like":62,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"c35f37f5e042d10ab519b2f44548d8c128727af5","tid":2326001,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ad7J50v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAd7J50v.jpg&h=d9c09dce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c2Rbvsm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc2Rbvsm.jpg&h=63481281&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CpgnB7B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCpgnB7B.jpg&h=375d9dd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開盒個葡汁香味就好誘人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋佢唔似普通葡汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係個汁入面食到有少少masala既香氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞皮夠香雞肉夠嫩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個著仔沙律好似轉咗做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n著蓉既比例多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口感上進步咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但個味我覺得淡咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以再濃少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落條尿道好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b907c899b4968eefa5f5cb6bb72e5ae42517e8ea","tid":2326001,"uid":207702,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:02:43.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e41295a68c95f616bfd6df73b8eb8e57ba2d74f","tid":2326001,"u